   <p xml:id="1" begin="00:00:05.567" end="00:00:08.537">&gt;&gt;&gt; IN THE BACK OF THE BOOK </p>
   <p xml:id="2" begin="00:00:06.768" end="00:00:10.038">SEGMENT TONIGHT, THE ACTOR AND </p>
