   <p xml:id="7" begin="00:00:16.478" end="00:00:21.049">AFTER ADDICTION NEARLY CAUSED </p>
   <p xml:id="8" begin="00:00:19.181" end="00:00:22.251">HIS LIFE BOBBY WAS SAVED AND </p>
   <p xml:id="9" begin="00:00:21.183" end="00:00:24.019">BACK IN ACTION ON STAGE.</p>
   <p xml:id="10" begin="00:00:22.384" end="00:00:29.358">BILL RECENTLY SPOKE WITH BILL </p>
   <p xml:id="11" begin="00:00:24.152" end="00:00:31.994">AND FAME, FORTUNE AND HIS NEWEST</p>
   <p xml:id="12" begin="00:00:29.491" end="00:00:32.327">BIOGRAPHY, &quot;TEEN IDOL ON THE </p>
