   <p xml:id="49" begin="00:01:39.595" end="00:01:43.099">&gt;&gt; THIS WHOLE PHENOMENON OCCURS </p>
   <p xml:id="50" begin="00:01:41.864" end="00:01:43.666">WHEN YOU'RE WHAT?</p>
   <p xml:id="51" begin="00:01:43.232" end="00:01:45.001">&gt;&gt; 17. </p>
   <p xml:id="52" begin="00:01:44.233" end="00:01:47.904">&gt;&gt; 17 YEARS OLD.</p>
   <p xml:id="53" begin="00:01:45.134" end="00:01:52.408">I HAD MY FIRST HIT RECORD THE </p>
   <p xml:id="54" begin="00:01:48.037" end="00:01:54.377">SUMMER OF 1959.</p>
   <p xml:id="55" begin="00:01:52.542" end="00:01:56.679">♪♪</p>
